item.title: Memories about unique properties of Durabolin types
item.description: Oftentimes people assume ND betters NPP and viceversa, in real life, there’s absolutely no contrast. The specific type active-life provides the option of choosing specs - Nandrolone Phenylpropionate serves for the obvious hardness, Nandrolone Decanoate restores and heals faster. Type can’t vary main qualities of the item, as inside ampule there’s Durabolin.
